{
  "id": "simple-token-trade",
  "title": "Simple Token Trade",
  "description": "Enables player-to-player and player-to-NPC trading of items and gold directly from the character sheet inventory.",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "url": "https://github.com/NomadODST/simple-token-trade",
  "manifest": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/NomadODST/simple-token-trade/main/module.json",
  "download": "https://github.com/NomadODST/simple-token-trade/releases/download/1.0.0/simple-token-trade.zip",
  "compatibility": {
    "minimum": "12",
    "verified": "12",
    "maximum": "13"
  },
  "authors": [
    {
      "name": "NomadODST",
      "url": "https://github.com/NomadODST"
    }
  ],
  "esmodules": [
    "scripts/namespace.js",
    "scripts/trade-session.js",
    "scripts/trade-socket.js",
    "scripts/trade-app.js",
    "scripts/inventory-trade.js"
  ],
  "styles": [
    "trade.css"
  ],
  "languages": [],
  "flags": {}
}
```

Die drei wichtigen Felder die gefehlt haben:

- **`url`** – Projektseite, wird in Foundry's Modulübersicht angezeigt
- **`manifest`** – die URL zu dieser `module.json` selbst, damit Foundry Updates erkennen kann
- **`download`** – direkter ZIP-Download, den Foundry zum Installieren verwendet

In Foundry kannst du das Modul jetzt über *Install Module → Manifest URL* mit diesem Link installieren:
```
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/NomadODST/simple-token-trade/main/module.json
